This is an Arduino project for a Midi Fighter type midi controller.  

Files
-----
midi_controller.ino - This is the main Arduino sketch.
midi.ino - Midi related functions can be found here.
shiftin.ino - Contains the function used to read the 4021 shift
register.

Templates to mount the 35mm arcade-style buttons used in the project can
be found under the *button_template* folder.

PCB schematic and board can be found under the *eagle* directory.
